Source: vast
Section: science
Priority: optional
Maintainer: ISIS Group (The friendly isis team) <gr_isis@cbs.mpg.de>
Build-Depends: libqwt5-qt4-dev, libqt4-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.1

Package: vast
Section: science
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libisiscore0 (>= 0.4.0), isis-qt4
Recommends: vast-timeplotter, vast-orientationcorrection, isisio0-vista, isisio0-nifti, isisio0-dicom, isisio0-gz-proxy, isisio0-tar-proxy
Description: vast is a viewer for medical image data. It supports all image formats
 that are supportet by the isis package. With version 0.1.0 these are the following:
 nifti, vista, dicom, tar.gz, raw, img, hdr.
 The viewer is capable of visualizing anatomical images, statistical images and functional images.

Package: vast-timeplotter
Section: science
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libqwt5-qt4, libisiscore0 (>= 0.4.0)
Description:  vast is a viewer for medical image data. It supports all image formats
 that are supportet by the isis package. With version 0.1.0 these are the following:
 nifti, vista, dicom, tar.gz, raw, img, hdr.
 The viewer is capable of visualizing anatomical images, statistical images and functional images.
 .
 This package provides a timeplotter-plugin for the vast viewer.

